@startuml
title Flusso Plant API - POST /v1/plants/search

actor Client as C
participant "Plant API BS (borepurposingmgmt)" as API_BS
participant "Plant Service BS (borepurposingmgmt)" as Service_BS
participant "Plant API MS (meRepurposingReg)" as API_MS
database "Database" as DB

C -> API_BS : POST /v1/plants/search\nBody: PlantSearchDTORequest {page, pageSize, sort[], ids[]}
activate API_BS

API_BS -> Service_BS : Invoca route interna SEARCH_PLANT
activate Service_BS

note right of Service_BS
HTTP_METHOD = POST
CONTENT_TYPE = application/json
end note

Service_BS -> API_MS : POST {meRepurposingRegEndPoint}/v1/plants/search\nBody: PlantSearchDTORequest {page, pageSize, sort[], ids[]}
activate API_MS

API_MS -> DB : Query di ricerca Plant con filtri  
DB --> API_MS : Risultato ricerca
API_MS --> Service_BS : - JSON Response 200 OK: WrapperPlantDTOResponse {stats, items[]}\n- Error Response 404 / 500
deactivate API_MS

Service_BS --> API_BS : Restituisce Response
deactivate Service_BS

API_BS --> C : - 200 OK (JSON Response)\n- 404 / 500 Error response
deactivate API_BS

@enduml
